.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.430b</biblScope> </bibl>), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> </bibl>(<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg010.perseus-grc1:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Art.\">Art.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">41</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg003.perseus-grc1:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prog.\">Prog.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23</biblScope></bibl>, al., cf. i p.cxx K.), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author></bibl>, and <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author></bibl>, also in Pap., <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phld.\">Phld.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ir.\">Ir.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">pp.27,28</biblScope> </bibl> W., and Inscr., <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">42(1).122.56</biblScope> </bibl> (Epid., <date TEIform=\"date\">iv B. C.</date>), and is doubtless the original form, which was altered in accordance with a supposed deriv. from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πνεῦμα</foreign> suggested by <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg037:476a:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Resp.\">Resp.<